\v 15 ∆ó ongg…®t bib…®r w…®ng…®r…®nd, re ama r…®ka andred twenti (120) r…®ga bobo na y…®pand wekenonj d…®k…®nd demb ongg…®t met…®nd, …® Petro onyitonj ongg…®t gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® d…®de ket yindonj da,  
\v 16 ‚ÄúKor nany d…®de y…®ngganwar! S…® b'ogla y…®na peba r…®r…®rk…®p rain r…®na re Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga Dawid…®mna tug…®m ke tulatula wum…®r yoramitonj Yudas…®m gatab yet re wang iyoyam awonj towan…®m yepiya re Yesund yokato neg…®r omnam.  
\v 17 Ton re s…®n k…®ma y…®pand ogeni r…®ga na y…®bnonj sowa w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® d…®de ton ongg…®tyam sowaina w…®ko w…®ng…®r…®nd kea y…®pa yingg yokatonj y…®r …®pkam.  
\v 18 (Aj…® ongg…®t r…®gat m…®ra wulk…®p yokatonj neg…®r k…®ma kaokao m…®le kena r…®na re ton Yesum p…®l…®nd yomn…®konj. ∆ó ket ongg…®t wulk…®p kena gou k…®pol yokatonj tin…®m. Ongg…®t kak ke ton ket mop ke mop ke g…®r…®g…®r…® sap otendonj, …® kom …®ny…®ny…®nd otendonj d…®de komkesa ti kom …®sark…®to.  
\v 19 ∆ó komkesa r…®ga wekenonj de Yerusalem taun wa, kea ongg…®tyam gatab wum…®r auk…®to, s…® ton ket …®temb gou k…®pol ny…® yoeko towainajog y…®t ke da ‚ÄòAkeldama‚Äô, y…®tkak nok ma yindeny da ‚ÄòKus k…®ma Gou K…®pol‚Äô.)  
