\m
\v 21-22 S…® ongg…®t paemb da men b'ogla yabagendu mera w…®ng…®r…®nd odede r…®ga yet re s…®n k…®ma yikenenonj komkesa w…®n…®nd r…®na re Yonggyam Yesu y…®bnenenonj sowa w…®ng…®r…®nd Yoan…®mna baptiso otomapu ke ng…®rpu de …®t re w…®n r…®denat re God Yesund yiyonj pumb wa mera p…®lke. S…® ton b'ogla y…®pa r…®ga, y…®r ungatayam tainy s…®n k…®ma y…®pand Tina utnyita gatab.‚Äù  
\v 23 Tina y…®t seg ke ton ket n…®mog r…®ga awaikito. Y…®pa re Yosep…®t, kwa ny…® da Barsaba yena re r…®gap kwa y…®pa ny…® ke yogenayo da Yusto, …® y…®pa re Matiyat.  
\v 24 Ongg…®t kak ke ton ket y…®r opmitto da, ‚ÄúSowa Yonggyam! Man wum…®r et komkesa r…®gaina gar. S…® ongg…®t n…®mog r…®ga w…®ng…®r…®nd y…®pa r…®ga nouyaene yena re man yobagendot.  
