\v 46 ∆ó ton ita bib…®r y…®pand nony menamena k…®ma y…®namet aband danda k…®ma b'eomenento. ∆ó ton ket ita gar ke utkunda r…®gaina met…®nd sana epk…®kenento Yesund nony iyenam, s…® ton ukoi sam k…®ma d…®de k…®lk…®p kesa nony menamena k…®ma owou awenento.  
