\p
\v 10 Ongg…®t w…®n…®nd y…®pa b'auyaena r…®ga ny…® da Ananiya y…®bnonj Damasko taun…®nd. ∆ó re ton liyalliyal y…®t yutkundonj Yonggyam…®nd, …® Ton ket tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúAnaniya-w…®i!‚Äù S…® todaka m…®ra yomnonj da, ‚ÄúOw…®, Yonggyam! Kon …®ta d…®k…®nd-o.‚Äù  
\v 11 S…® Yonggyam tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúUtnyite, …® menon yokate ongg…®t nya wa ogenaya da, ‚ÄòD…®md…®mjog Nya‚Äô! ∆ó d…®de ra ket man meket dor Yudas…®m met wa, man …®ta odaret dor y…®pa Tarso tunggam ny…® da Saul. Ton re y…®r e opmiteny.  
\v 12 ∆ó ton kea liyalliyal y…®pa r…®ga y…®r yong ny…® da Ananiya, …® kwa ton y…®r yong da …®temb r…®ga Ananiya ke ongg…®t met wa b'…®gar…®k …® y…®m aramisiny ti p…®l…®nd tin y…®r …®pangendam.‚Äù  
\v 13 ∆ó ket Ananiya m…®ra yomnonj da, ‚ÄúYonggyam! Kon ke jogjog y…®t utkundeneninond ongg…®t r…®gam gatab r…®na re ton Moina y…®na r…®ga neg…®r amn…®keneninonj Yerusalem taun…®nd.  
\v 14 ∆ó kwa ton kea y…®na mopyam s…® r…®ga wa p…®lke danda yokatonj da ton komkesa r…®ga imda teyeniny yena re Moina ny…® k…®ma agenairanj, d…®de kea ikonj d…®k…®nd Damasko wa ongg…®tyam neg…®r w…®ko omn…®kam.‚Äù  
\v 15 Aj…® Yonggyam tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúMenon yokate ti p…®lwa! Mop nok…®p Kon ke ongg…®t r…®gand yobagendond Koina w…®ko r…®gam yet ra Koina y…®t opurena teyeneniny. S…® ton opima ukoijog beb…®g turowateniny Koina ny…® warabag omn…®kam God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga wa, …® king wa, …® d…®de kwa Israel r…®ga wa p…®lwa.  
\v 16 ∆ó Kon …®ta tin ouyaeny…®n r…®dede w…®p e ton b'ogla b'asowa takateniny Koina ny…® map ra ton ongg…®tyam w…®ko omn…®ka teyeniny.‚Äù  
\v 17 Seg re ket Ananiya menon yokatonj, …® Yudas…®m met wa b'…®garonj. ∆ó ket ton Saul…®m p…®l…®nd y…®m aramitonj d…®de yomnonj da, ‚ÄúKor y…®nggan Saul! Man ke y…®r yongot Yonggyam Yesund nyaw…®nd, re man metkot d…®k…®nd. S…® Ton…®temb ken n…®tm…®kis men y…®r …®pangendam d…®de Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga ke men y…®ndang…®r omnam.‚Äù  
\v 18 ∆ó odenja ket tina y…®rk…®p ke jup p…®la gasa kea ogomk…®to. ∆ó ket tina y…®r …®pangendonda. Seg ket ton utnyitonj, …® ket baptiso yokatonj.  
\v 19 ∆ó re ton ket owou awinonj, ton ket kwa kea danda akasinonj.  
\s1 Saul…®mna P…®tap…®ta Omna Y…®t Damaskond  
\p Seg ton ket b'auyaena r…®ga k…®ma y…®bnonj n…®nda bib…®r k…®ma de Damasko wa.  
\v 20 Seg ton ket odenja yikonj Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met wa, …® b'atomonj p…®tap…®ta omnenam Yesum gatab y…®t da, ‚ÄúYesu re God…®mna B'…®ga e.‚Äù  
\v 21 S…® komkesa r…®ga yepiya re tina y…®t utkundeno, ton k…®d kesa na aena wuwenonj, d…®de b'arkena wuwenonj da, ‚ÄúMa ma …®nte j…® r…®ga yet re gar ke utkunda r…®ga neg…®r omn…®ka eyeninonj Yerusalem taun…®nd yepiya re …®temb R…®ga Yesund yewangaeneno? Ma ma ton nok mana ikonj d…®k…®nd da …®denat ton Yesund gar ke utkunda r…®ga y…®m…®nd imda teyeniny, d…®de teyeniny y…®na mopyam s…® r…®ga wa p…®lwa s…®b…®bmet…®nd oramkam?‚Äù  
\v 22 Aj…® Saul mogjog danda oik…®ndena k…®ma …®m…®njog…®m y…®t p…®tap…®ta yomnenonj da, ‚Äú∆ótemb Yesu re Keriso e.‚Äù S…® ongg…®t penaemb Ju r…®ga yepiya re wekenonj de Damasko wa, nony menamena kesa auka wuwenonj tina y…®t gou wa omnenam.   
\p
\v 23 ∆ó jogjog bib…®r seg ke, Ju r…®gap y…®pand omn…®kto, d…®de ket g…®lg…®l y…®samko Saul…®nd ongandam.  
\v 24 S…® ton ita bib…®r d…®de s…®w…®ny tin nya owama yiyeneno tin ongandam komkesa taun mora nata r…®ngkena re r…®ga wuwenenonj ongg…®t taun kara bora wa b'…®garenam o kara bora ke opendenam. Aj…® Saul kea wum…®r yokatenonj ongg…®tyam towaina …®samki y…®t gatab.  
\v 25 S…® daka y…®pa s…®w…®ny…®nd, tina b'auyaena r…®gap ukoi ga wa tin yoramito d…®de ket inka yiyo taun kara kumb ke de bau wa.   
\s1 Saul…®mna W…®mena Yerusalem…®nd  
\p
\v 26 S…® ongg…®t kak ke ket, Saul yikonj Yerusalem taun wa. ∆ó ton pop b'atonkitonj b'auyaena r…®ga k…®ma y…®pand awow…®m, aj…® komkesa r…®ga re maka tin …®m…®njog…®m yomneno da, ‚ÄúTon re y…®pa b'auyaena r…®ga e.‚Äù S…® tin moga na uwada yiyeno.  
\v 27 Aj…® re Banaba …®m…®njog wum…®r awonj ti gatab, ton ket tin yiyonj de …®tm…®kitijog r…®ga wa p…®lwa. ∆ó ton ket ten wum…®r amneninonj r…®ja na re Saul Yonggyam…®nd y…®r yongonj nyaw…®nd, d…®de r…®ja na re Yonggyam tin y…®t yomnenonj, …® d…®de kwa r…®ja na re Saul Yesumna ny…® k…®ma moga kesa God ma y…®t p…®tap…®ta yomnenonj de Damasko wa.  
\v 28 Seg ket Saul ton k…®ma b'eomkitonj d…®de y…®pand g…®lg…®l yikenenonj Yerusalem taun…®nd, …® d…®de ket Yonggyam…®m ny…® k…®ma moga kesa God ma y…®t p…®tap…®ta omnena yiyenenonj.  
\v 29 Ongg…®t w…®n…®nd, ton kwa kea y…®t apureninonj Grik y…®tam Ju r…®ga wa p…®lwa d…®de ket ton k…®ma y…®t b'ugwatena wuwenonj. S…® ongg…®t penaemb ton ket tin otonkena yiyeneno ongandam.  
\v 30 ∆ó re gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar…®p wum…®r yokato ongg…®tyam ti gatab y…®t, ton ket tin yiyo de Kaisareya wa, d…®de ket y…®tm…®kito de tina ukendipu tungg Tarso taun wa.   
\p
\v 31 ∆óngkek ket kupka Yuda …® Galili …® d…®de Samariya w…®ng…®r…®nd, sosi re kea ng…®mbla w…®ng…®r nat wekenonj, d…®de danda k…®ma ow…®nk…®to. ∆ó kwa ket Yonggyam…®nd moga yuwadeneno, d…®de Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat ugowa eyeneninonj. S…® ongg…®t penaemb Yesu ma sosi ukoi warabag auka yikonj.   
\s1 Petro Aineand Y…®sakendonj  
\p
\v 32 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd, Petro menon yokatenonj komkesa gatab nata, …® ket kwa yikonj de Lida taun wa, d…®de adarinonj y…®na r…®ga yepiya re wekenonj ongg…®t taun…®nd.  
\v 33 ∆ó ton ket yodaronj y…®pa r…®ga ny…® da Ainea. Ton re d…®m…®r kopa ma pena eit (8) kemag k…®ma yutungi y…®bnenenonj kasand.  
\v 34 ∆ó Petro ket tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúAinea! Yesu Keriso ke men m…®sakenj. Utnyite d…®de moina kasa yongonjene!‚Äù Seg ton ket odenja utnyitonj.  
\v 35 S…® komkesa r…®ga yepiya re Lida taun…®nd d…®de Saron taun…®nd wekenonj kea tin y…®r yongo, d…®de gar engento Yonggyam…®m p…®lwa, …® d…®de ket Tin gar ke utkunda ke yokato.   
\s1 Dorkamna Yilo Okati Y…®t  
\p
\v 36 ∆ó y…®pa b'auyaena kongga Tabita w…®bnonj de Yopa taun wa. ∆ó ti Grik ke engendi ny…® re Dorka. Ton ma sobijog na r…®ga wa b'og…®l w…®ko amn…®kaeneninonj, d…®de ingaena gasa kesa r…®ga kear amn…®keneninonj.  
\v 37 ∆ó re Petro y…®bnonj Lida wa, Tabita kea kopa yokatonj d…®de ket uj awonj. S…® r…®gap ujg…®m gony weauko, …® wiyo, d…®de woramito tina met n…®mog…®m ror kok wa.  
\v 38 ∆ó Lida taun re ma p…®n na y…®bnonj Yopa taun ke. S…® re b'auyaena r…®gap utkundo da Petro ama de Lida taun wa, ton ket n…®mog r…®ga etm…®kito ti p…®lwa. ∆ó re ton tin yodaronda, ton ket Petrond …®l yongkonda da, ‚ÄúGoro kwa b'at…®gnen…®m! Wuy…®n-a y…®pand sowa tungg wa!‚Äù  
\v 39 ∆ó Petro ket utnyita nena awonj, d…®de ket menon yokatonj ton k…®ma. Re ton ket opendonj, r…®gap tin yiyo de n…®mog…®m ror kok wa r…®k…®nd re Dorkamna ujg…®m w…®bnawonj. ∆ó komkesa mik konggap Petrom wus…®nd ow…®nk…®to, …® yii k…®ma tin ouyaukura yiyeno b'engabenga kob…®rg…®m r…®na re Dorka amn…®kawainonj, re ton yilo w…®bnonj.  
\v 40 ∆ó Petro ket komkesa r…®ga eaukeninonj bau wa, …® ket kumop b'amkonj d…®de y…®r opmitonj. Seg re ket ton b'engendonj ujg…®m w…®p wa, …® ket yindonj da, ‚ÄúTabita! Utnyite!‚Äù ∆ó ton ket tina y…®r apngendonj, …® Petrond y…®r…®k y…®njomkitonj, …® d…®de ton ket omitonj.  
\v 41 ∆ó Petro y…®m ke tin wokatonj, d…®de wurowatonj onyitam. ∆ó ton ket ara emokinonj y…®na r…®ga d…®de mik kongga, d…®de ket ti yilond wiyonj towa p…®lwa.  
\v 42 ∆ó komkesa Yopa taun r…®ga kea ongg…®tyam gatab wum…®r yokateno, d…®de jogjog r…®ga Yonggyam…®nd gar ke utkunda ke yokato.  
\v 43 ∆ó Petro omanda Yopa taun…®nd y…®bnonj y…®pa r…®ga k…®ma ny…® da Simon yet re b'angga g…®m ke gasa amn…®keneninonj.   
\c 10  
\s1 Korneliyomna Petrond ∆óngauka Y…®t  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó y…®pa Roma r…®ga y…®bnonj Kaisareya taun wa ny…® da Korneliyo. Ton re andred (100) Roma geja r…®ga mopyam na, …® r…®gap ongg…®tyam geja r…®ga bobo ny…® yogenayo da, ‚ÄúItaliya Geja R…®ga Bobo‚Äù.  
\v 2 ∆ó ton God…®nd yewangaenenonj, d…®de God…®nd ewangaya Ju r…®ga waina m…®le amn…®keneninonj y…®pand komkesa ti r…®gawar k…®ma yepiya re wekenonj ti met…®nd. ∆ó ton kea ita w…®n…®nd kear amn…®keneninonj ingaena gasa kesa r…®ga, d…®de kwa ton ita w…®n…®nd God…®m p…®lwa y…®r opmitenenonj.  
\v 3 ∆ó y…®pa bib…®r…®nd s…®mana tri (3) k…®lok…®nd, ton p…®tak…®p…®nd liyalliyal y…®r yongonj God…®mna aneru. ∆ó ket ongg…®t anerut ikonj ti p…®lwa, …® yomnonj da, ‚ÄúKorneliyo!‚Äù  
\v 4 ∆ó re ton y…®r p…®np…®n yomn…®konj anerund, ton moga na awonj. S…® yerkitonj da, ‚ÄúYonggyam! Nangga e?‚Äù ∆ó aneru m…®ra yomnonj da, ‚ÄúGod opima moina y…®r opmita utkundeneniny, …® kwa opima moina kear b'amnena m…®le y…®r ongong eyeniny. S…® God opima nony…®nd owama eyeniny ongg…®tyam moina m…®le.  
\v 5 S…® man otade r…®ga tetm…®kisiny…®t de Yopa wa …®ngaukam Simon…®nd, yena re kwa ny…® yogenai da Petro.  
\v 6 ∆ótemb r…®ga re obayam e y…®b…®m de b'angga g…®m ke gasa omn…®ka r…®ga Simon…®m met wa. ∆ó tina met re s…®pa yuru nate y…®b…®m.‚Äù  
\v 7 ∆ó re ket aneru yet re tin y…®t yomnenonj, Korneliyond ket y…®raronj, ton ket ara emokinonj n…®mog ti met w…®ko r…®ga d…®de y…®pa geja r…®ga. ∆ó …®temb geja r…®ga re God ma obagendi kesa r…®ga na aj…® y…®pa b'og…®l God…®nd ewangaya r…®ga na y…®bnonj Korneliyomna nony …®jai r…®ga w…®ng…®r…®nd yepiya re ton k…®ma wuswus wekenenonj.  
\v 8 ∆ó re ket ton tuwonj Korneliyom p…®lwa, ton ten b'obog…®l wum…®r amneninonj ongg…®tyam komkesa y…®t r…®na re ti p…®l…®nd aukonj. Seg ket ton etm…®kisinonj de Yopa taun wa.   
\s1 Petromna Liyalliyal Y…®r Ongong gatab Y…®t  
\p
\v 9 S…® ongg…®t nowa r…®gap menon yokato Yopa taun wa. ∆ó …®spari ke ket, re ton Yopa wus wa auk…®to, Petro ket yikonj tou kesa met papkak kumb wa y…®r opmitam lomt…®k gatab…®nd.  
\v 10 ∆ó re Petro y…®r opmitenonj, ton ket ma sobijog na owoupa awonj. ∆ó re Petro owou y…®r ungawand y…®bnonj, ti nonony kesand y…®pa liyalliyal gasa aukonj ti w…®p…®nd.  
\v 11 ∆ó re ton y…®r yongonj wub kumb …®pangendand, ton kwa kea y…®r yongonj y…®pa ukoi kob…®rg…®m p…®la gasa r…®na re powa (4) wug…®nd …®job…®ki gou wa inka ikonj.  
\v 12 ∆ó komkesa powa (4) p…®skak k…®ma b'angga, …® mukak ke gow…®nd menamena b'angga, …® d…®de wub kumb…®nd ngena kea wekenonj de ongg…®t gasa kumb…®nd. Komkesa re k…®lk…®l gasa na r…®na re God maka Ju r…®ga enj…®keninonj ongong…®m gog y…®t r…®r…®r…®nd.  
\v 13 ∆ó ti p…®lwa ara ikonj da, ‚ÄúPetro! Utnyite! Epoine d…®de angine!‚Äù  
\v 14 Aj…® Petro daka yomnonj da, ‚ÄúYonggyam! Makwa r…®r…®r e! Kon maka angeneninond odede b'angga r…®na re God gog amninonj da y…®na omni kesa im d…®de k…®lk…®l im.‚Äù  
\v 15 ∆ó ket n…®mog…®m ara ikonj ti p…®lwa da, ‚ÄúGod kea ongg…®tyam b'angga komkesa k…®lk…®p kesa amninonj. S…® man goro tapurenin…®m da y…®na omni kesa im d…®de k…®lk…®l im!‚Äù  
\v 16 ∆ó re odede nowapyam p…®tap…®ta aenonj, odenja ket ongg…®tyam gasa wub kumb wa …®tendonj.   
\p
\v 17 ∆ó Petro ti gar…®nd nony…®k b'amdenonj ongg…®tyam liyalliyal gasa gatab r…®na re ton y…®r yongonj, aj…® nonys…®ps…®p na aukonj da, ‚ÄúNangga ma j…® gasa aw…®k?‚Äù ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd daka Korneliyomna …®tm…®kiti r…®gap r…®ga erkena eyento da, ‚ÄúRokate Simon…®mna met?‚Äù ng…®rpu ton ket yodaro tina met, …® ket ow…®nk…®to tina met kara morand.  
\v 18 ∆ó ton ket ara wuwenonj, …® arkitto da, ‚ÄúW…®i, r…®ka …®ta d…®k…®nd Simon are yena re ny…® yogenai da Petro?‚Äù  
\v 19 Ongg…®t w…®n…®nd Petro omanda nony menamena omn…®kand y…®bnonj ongg…®tyam tina liyalliyal y…®r ongi gasa gatab. ∆ó odedend daka ket Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúY…®r de, nowa r…®gap mena oraka miyenyi.  
\v 20 S…® man utnyite, d…®de gou wa meke! ∆ó d…®de meket dor ton k…®ma! Goro nonys…®ps…®p tauk…®m dor, mop nok…®p Kon…®t ten etm…®kisiny…®m…®n!‚Äù  
\v 21 ∆ó re Petro gou wa yikonj de ongg…®t r…®ga wa p…®lwa, ton ket amninonj da, ‚ÄúW…®i, kon …®temb j…® r…®ga yena re w…®n oraka yiyenya. S…® w…®n nangga mop paim tuy…®t?‚Äù  
\v 22 ∆ó todaka ket m…®ra yomno da, ‚ÄúWan andred (100) Roma geja r…®ga mopyam Korneliyot n…®tm…®kisiny…®m mor p…®lwa. Ton re d…®md…®mjog r…®ga e d…®de God…®nd ewangaya God ma obagendi kesa r…®ga e, s…® komkesa Ju r…®ga wum…®rjog im tina m…®le. S…® ongg…®t paemb tin ket y…®snaenenyi. ∆ó kwa daka y…®pa y…®na anerut tin yingawonj men …®ngaukam ti met wa, d…®de y…®tkak utkundam nangga im ra man tapureniny…®t. S…® s…®n opimemb ket tuy…®n.‚Äù  
\v 23 S…® ongg…®t penaemb Petro ten engaukinonj w…®ng…®r wa menon…®m, d…®de obai amninonj.  
\s1 Petro Yikonj Korneliyomna Met wa  
\p ∆ó …®spari ke ket Petro utnyitonj, …® ket ton k…®ma yiwatonj. D…®de kwa Yopa ke gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar w…®ng…®r…®nd n…®nda r…®ga daka kea wuwonj y…®pand ton k…®ma.  
\v 24 ∆ó …®spari ke ket Petro Kaisareya taun kara wa b'…®garonj. ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd Korneliyo daka kea tina gu r…®ga d…®de tina wuswus r…®ga ara emokinonj, …® y…®pand b'eomto ti met…®nd. ∆ó ton ket Petro d…®de ton k…®ma r…®ga y…®r ungauk…®to.  
\v 25 ∆ó re Petro Korneliyomna met wa b'…®garonj, Korneliyo ket tin w…®pw…®p yomnonj, …® ket b'…®snawa k…®ma egomendonj ti p…®s w…®p…®nd, d…®de ket kumsos b'amkonj.  
\v 26 Aj…® Petro tin yutnyitonj d…®de yomnonj da, ‚ÄúUtnyite! Koda re y…®pa r…®ga en odede man re d…®de.‚Äù  
\v 27 ∆ó Petro ket y…®t b'usenena k…®ma b'…®garonj ton k…®ma, d…®de ket ukoi r…®ga bobo adarinonj.  
\v 28 S…® ton ten amninonj da, ‚ÄúW…®da wum…®rjog im sowaina gog. S…® …®ja imemb j…® sowaina gog m…®le da Ju r…®ga ma opima w…®n, God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga k…®ma b'eteomkenanj, …® b'at…®darenanj y…®t b'usenenam o diyam awow…®m o w…®menam. Aj…® God kea ken nouyawonj da, ‚ÄòGoro yena r…®ga ogenay…®m da ton re y…®na omni kesa e o k…®lk…®l e.‚Äô  
\v 29 S…® ongg…®t paemb re w…®n ken n…®ngaukonda, kon makwa nangga y…®t na apureninond, aj…® kon menon nena na awond. S…® ongg…®t paemb kon kwa tarkisiny…®n da w…®n nangga mop pena n…®ngaukonda?‚Äù  
\v 30 ∆ó Korneliyo ket m…®ra yomnonj da, ‚ÄúRe y…®to nowa bib…®r teteautondam seg ket ongg…®tyam bib…®r…®nd odede tri (3) k…®lok s…®mana gatab…®nd, kon y…®r opmitenond kor met…®nd. Odedend ket y…®pa b…®lb…®ljog kob…®rg…®m b'ikoki r…®gat onyitonj kor w…®p…®nd.  
\v 31 ∆ó ton ket nomnonj da, ‚ÄòKorneliyo! God opima moina y…®r opmitena utkundeneniny, …® kwa opima moina kear b'amnena m…®le nony…®nd owama eyeniny.  
\v 32 S…® ongg…®t paemb man r…®ga tetm…®kisiny…®t Yopa wa Simon…®nd …®ngaukam yena re kwa ny…® yogenai da Petro. Ton re obayam e y…®b…®m b'angga g…®m ke gasa omn…®ka r…®ga ti ny…®mad Simon…®mna met…®nd, …® …®temb re met s…®pa yuru nate y…®b…®m.‚Äô  
\v 33 S…® ongg…®t penaemb kon odenja r…®ga etm…®kisinond men orontam. S…® otomantijog e r…®na re man metket. S…® s…®n komkesa d…®k…®nd b'eomkisindam God…®m w…®p nasim. ∆ó s…®n singi im utkundenam komkesa y…®tkak r…®na re Yonggyam men mingau s…®n wum…®r omnenam.‚Äù   
\s1 Petromna P…®tap…®ta Omni Y…®tkak Korneliyom Met…®nd  
\p
\v 34 ∆ó ket Petro b'atomonj y…®t opurena da, ‚ÄúKon otade …®m…®njog ke wum…®r yokas…®n da God ma …®ta bu b'iyena m…®le yomn…®keneny odede …®t re da Ton y…®pa tab Ju r…®ga nena y…®rkokar agoniny.  
\v 35 Aj…® God y…®rkokar agoniny re komkesa b'engabenga y…®tam r…®ga wa mim yepim re Tin ewangaya yiyenyi d…®de Ti p…®lwa neg…®r kesa d…®md…®mjog m…®le amn…®kenenanj.  
\v 36 W…®n wum…®r im j…® da God Tina b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t y…®tm…®kitonj Israel r…®ga wa p…®lwa na. S…® …®ja naemb j…® ongg…®tyam y…®tkak opurenam yotomonj da Yesu Keriso ng…®mbla yoramitonj God d…®de r…®ga wa ganggand, …® …®ngkaemb ongg…®t ng…®mbla k…®ma God ma b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t p…®tap…®ta aena yikeny komkesa r…®ga wa p…®lwa. S…® …®temb re Yesu, ma Ju r…®ga wa nena ma Yonggyam e, aj…® komkesa r…®ga wa Yonggyam e.  
\v 37 ∆ó kwa w…®n kea wum…®r im da re Yoan engenda baptiso gatab y…®t p…®tap…®ta yomnenonj, Yesu ket ongg…®tyam bage y…®t iyena w…®ko yotomonj Galili eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd, …® …®ngkek ket kupka Yuda eriya nata opurena yiyenonj.  
\v 38 God kea Najaret tunggam Yesund Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga ke d…®de danda ke y…®ndang…®r yomn…®konj. S…® Yesu ket yikenonj komkesa gatab wa, …® b'og…®l w…®ko omn…®ka eyeninonj, …® d…®de komkesa r…®ga b'og…®l amn…®keninonj yepiya re Satanamna danda w…®rand wekenonj. Mop nok…®p God re kea omanda y…®bnenenonj Yesu k…®ma.  
\v 39 ∆ó s…®n re y…®r ungatayam r…®ga im komkesa m…®le gatab r…®na re ton amn…®kinonj Yuda eriyand d…®de Yerusalem…®nd. R…®gap tin ket y…®dr…®ko wul b'agbag…®nd d…®de yongando.  
\v 40 ∆ó re ket nowam bib…®r yokatonj, God tin yutnyitonj uj ke. D…®de ket God Tin y…®r ongong…®m p…®tap…®ta yomnenonj r…®ga wa p…®lwa.  
\v 41 ∆ó God tin p…®tap…®ta yomnenonj re ma komkesa r…®ga wa p…®lwa na, aj…® sowa p…®lwa nena na yena re God s…®n nobag…®kinonj y…®r ungatayam…®m. S…® re ton utnyitonj uj ke, s…®n kea Ton k…®ma y…®pand diyam aukenentondam d…®de ny…® anaikenentondam.  
\v 42 ∆ó Ton…®t ket s…®n ningainonj p…®tap…®ta omnenam r…®ga wa p…®lwa d…®de usenenam y…®r ungata y…®t da, ‚Äò∆ótemb re Yesu b'…®sag…®kayam e yena re God yobagendonj …®sag…®kam yilo r…®ga d…®de uj r…®ga.‚Äô  
\v 43 ∆ó komkesa bageyam…®p toda kwa kea ongg…®tyam Yesum gatab y…®r ungata y…®t usenena eyento da, ‚ÄòKomkesa r…®gap yepiya ra Tin gar ke utkunda ke okasi, God opima towaina neg…®r m…®le aw…®r tamn…®kainy Tina danda ny…® ke.‚Äô‚Äù   
\s1 Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga Inkonj God ma Obag…®ki kesa R…®ga Wa p…®l…®nd  
\p
\v 44 ∆ó re Petro ongg…®tyam y…®tkak usenenainonj, Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga kea ket igurkonj komkesa r…®ga wa p…®l…®nd yepiya re utkundento ongg…®tyam y…®tkak.  
\v 45-46 ∆ó …®ngkenaemb ton ket b'engabenga y…®t apurento d…®de ket ukoi kana God…®nd esourena yiyeno. S…® gar ke utkunda Ju r…®gap yepiya re God ma obag…®ki t…®r…®r omni mal wug…®m …®pka m…®le yokato, ton kea Petro k…®ma y…®pand tuwonj …® y…®r yongo ongg…®tyam m…®le. Seg ton ket ma sobijog na k…®d kesa aena wuwenonj, mop nok…®p Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat kea Tina yiyag wurar …®gmarka yiyenonj God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga wa p…®l…®nd. Odedend Petro yindonj da,  
\v 47 ‚ÄúOngg…®t r…®gap kemb Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga yokasi men re d…®de, s…® yete r…®r…®r e men ogoka nitiyeniny towan…®m ny…® ke baptiso okawam?‚Äù  
\v 48 S…® Petro ket ton k…®ma meni r…®ga engainonj ten baptiso omn…®kam Yesu Kerisomna ny…® k…®ma. ∆ó re baptiso omn…®ka seg awonj, r…®gap Petrond y…®gekito ton k…®ma w…®menam n…®nda bib…®r k…®ma.   
\c 11  
\s1 Petro Yerusalem…®nd P…®tap…®ta Yomnonj Tina Omn…®ki gatab Y…®t  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó …®tm…®kitijog r…®gap d…®de gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar…®p yepiya re Yuda eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd wekenonj, kea utkundeno da God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®gap re kea toda God ma y…®t gar ke utkunda ke yokateno.  
\v 2 S…® ongg…®t penaemb re Petro yikonj Yerusalem taun wa, n…®nda gar ke utkunda Ju r…®gap yepiya re God ma obagendi t…®r…®r omni mal wug…®m …®pka m…®le yokato, Petrond neg…®r g…®m yomn…®ko.  
\v 3 ∆ó yomno da, ‚ÄúMan b'…®garot re God ma obagendi t…®r…®r omni mal wug…®m …®pki kesa r…®ga waina met wa, d…®de ket ton k…®ma diyam awot.‚Äù  
\v 4 S…® Petro daka ket es…®pkenainonj komkesa y…®tkak otomapu ke de undwatapu wa.  
\v 5 S…® ton odede yindonj da, ‚ÄúRe kon y…®r opmitena nekenond Yopa taun…®nd, kon nonony kesand y…®pa liyalliyal gasa y…®r yongond. S…® y…®pa ukoi kob…®rg…®m p…®la gasa powa (4) wug…®nd …®job…®ki na y…®bnonj wub kumb…®nd, …® ket inka ikonj pumb ke ng…®rpu de kor p…®lwa.  
\v 6 Re kon b'obog…®l y…®r…®k eyeninond ongg…®tyam gasa, kon kea y…®r anginond powa (4) p…®skak k…®ma ongeni b'angga …® t…®bam b'angga …® mukak ke gow…®nd menamena b'angga …® d…®de wub…®nd ngena. Komkesa re k…®lk…®l gasa na r…®na re God maka Ju r…®ga enj…®keneninonj ongong…®m gog y…®t r…®r…®r…®nd.  
\v 7 ∆ó odedend kon ket ara utkundond. ∆ó odede nomnonj da, ‚ÄòPetro! Utnyite! Epoine d…®de angine!‚Äô  
\v 8 S…® kodaka ket yomnond da, ‚ÄòKor Yonggyam! Makwa r…®r…®r e! Kon makwa ke y…®pa odede y…®na omni kesa o k…®lk…®l b'angga koina tu bora wa y…®garond ongong…®m.‚Äô  
\v 9 ∆ó ket wub kumb ke n…®mog…®m ara ikonj, d…®de m…®ra nomnonj da, 'God kea ongg…®tyam b'angga komkesa k…®lk…®p kesa amn…®kinonj. S…® man goro tapurenin…®m da y…®na omni kesa im o k…®lk…®l im.‚Äô  
\v 10 ∆ó re odede nowapyam p…®tap…®ta aenonj, odenja ket ongg…®tyam b'angga k…®ma kupkakupka gasa b'usaya …®tendonj wub kumb wa.  
\v 11 ∆ó odedend ket nowa r…®ga opekto ongg…®t met wa r…®k…®nd re kon n…®bnond. Y…®pa r…®gat ten etm…®kisinonj kor p…®lwa Kaisareya taun ke.  
\v 12 ∆ó re ton nodaro, Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat ket nomnonj da, ‚ÄòTon k…®ma meket! Goro nonys…®ps…®p tauk…®m!‚Äô S…® opi re d…®k…®nd siks (6) gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar todaka kea kon k…®ma wuwonj ongg…®t r…®ga ma met wa ongg…®t taun…®nd, d…®de ket s…®n b'…®gartondam met w…®ng…®r wa.  
\v 13 ∆ó ton ket s…®n wum…®r nomninonj da ton y…®pa God ma aneru onyiti y…®r yongonj tina met…®nd, …® ongg…®t anerut tin odede yomnonj da, ‚ÄòR…®ga tetm…®kisiny…®t Yopa wa, d…®de Simon…®nd …®ngauket yena re kwa ny…® yogenai da Petro!  
\v 14 Ton …®ta mutusenenainy God ma y…®t, d…®de ongg…®tyam tina opureni y…®tkak kaim w…®n y…®rkokar okatenya, man d…®de komkesa r…®ga yepim re wekeny moina met…®nd.‚Äô  
\v 15 Seg re kon y…®t b'atomond, odedend Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga igurka yikenonj towa p…®l…®nd odede w…®p r…®ngmena re otomapu ke Ton mera p…®l…®nd igurkonj.  
\v 16 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd, kon ket Yonggyam…®mna y…®tkak nony…®k eyeninonj r…®na re ton yindonj odede da, ‚ÄòYoan ny…® kena r…®ga baptiso amn…®kinonj, aj…® w…®n Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga kae baptiso okatenya.‚Äô  
\v 17 Re men Yonggyam Yesu Kerisond gar ke yokatonda, God kea mera yiyag wurar nokainonj. ∆ó God re kea towada akainonj ongg…®tyam y…®paina yiyag wurar odede y…®pa w…®p mera p…®lwa re d…®de. Kon re y…®pa r…®gajog en. S…® r…®dede e kon God ma w…®ko ogoka iyeny…®n?‚Äù  
\v 18 ∆ó re r…®gap utkundento ongg…®tyam y…®tkak, ton mumakesa na wekenonj, d…®de ket God…®nd ewangaya yiyeno odede y…®t k…®ma da, ‚ÄúS…® …®m…®njog e. God re kea gar engenda m…®le Tina obag…®ki kesa r…®ga wa akainonj towan…®m y…®rkokar okatam.‚Äù   
\s1 Antiyok Sosi  
\p
\v 19 ∆ó re ukoi neg…®r k…®ma b'…®dgotnena p…®ta awonj Stepanomna uj kak ke, gar ke utkunda r…®ga wetaweta auka wuwenonj komkesa gatab wa. ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd n…®nda r…®ga re kea wuwenonj ng…®rpu de Poinikiya eriya wa, …® Kipriyo ailan wa, …® d…®de Antiyok taun wa. Re ton wuwenonj, ton ket Ju r…®ga wa nena mana God ma b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t p…®tap…®ta omnena eyenawo.  
\v 20 ∆ó towa w…®ng…®r…®nd n…®nda Kipriyo tunggam d…®de Kurene tunggam wuwenonj Antiyok taun wa. ∆ó ton ket God ma obag…®ki kesa Grik r…®ga wa towada kea kwa p…®tap…®ta omnena eyenawo Yonggyam Yesum gatab God ma b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t.  
\v 21 ∆ó Yonggyam kea towa p…®l…®nd tina danda y…®m aramkinonj ten y…®m okawam. S…® ma y…®pa k…®ma r…®gapiya gar engento, d…®de ket Yesund gar ke utkunda ke yokato, …® d…®de Tin ket y…®mta yundoko.  
\v 22 ∆ó ongg…®tyam towa gatab y…®d…®r y…®t re kea warabag aukonj, …® Yerusalem sosi r…®gap kea utkundeno ongg…®tyam y…®t. S…® ongg…®t penaemb ket Banaband y…®tm…®kito Antiyok taun wa.  
\v 23 ∆ó re ton opendonj de Antiyok taun wa, ton kea y…®r anginonj b'og…®l m…®le r…®na re gar ke utkunda r…®gap God…®mna wurar ke omn…®ka eyento. S…® ongg…®t penaemb ton ket gar sam awonj, d…®de ton ket komkesa r…®ga danda k…®ma ugoinonj da, ‚ÄúW…®n waina gar kupkakupka taramkindam Yonggyam…®m p…®l…®nd Tin y…®mta undokam.‚Äù  
\v 24 Banaba re b'og…®l r…®ga e, d…®de Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga ke y…®ndang…®r omni r…®ga e, …® d…®de ton re danda k…®ma gar ke utkunda r…®ga e. S…® ongg…®t penaemb ket ma sobijog r…®ga bobo na auka wuwenonj Yonggyam…®nd gar ke utkundam.  
\v 25 S…® ton ket yikonj Tarso wa Saul…®nd orakam.  
\v 26 ∆ó re ton tin yodaronj, ton ket tin yiyonj de Antiyok wa. ∆ó …®ngkenaemb ket Banaba ake Saul sosi r…®ga k…®ma y…®pand b'eomkenenonda kupka y…®pa kemag k…®ma. ∆ó d…®de ket ukoi r…®ga bobo ouyaena eyeninonda. S…® omandemb Antiyok taun…®nd r…®gap yiyata k…®ma ongg…®tyam b'auyaena r…®ga odede ny…® agenaito da ‚ÄúKerisomna R…®ga‚Äù.   
\p
\v 27 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd kea n…®nda bageyam tuwonj Yerusalem taun ke de Antiyok taun wa.  
\v 28 ∆ó Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat towa w…®ng…®r…®nd y…®pa bageyam ny…® da Agabo yingawonj y…®pa gasa r…®ga wa wum…®r omnam. S…® Agabo ket onyitonj, d…®de ten wum…®r amninonj da, ‚ÄúUkoi owoupa w…®n …®ta ik dem komkesa Roma kantri w…®ng…®r…®nd.‚Äù ∆ó …®temb owoupa w…®n p…®ta awonj re odenat re Klaudiyo Roma mopyam king yeb…®m.  
\v 29 S…® b'auyaena r…®gap singi auto y…®m okawam gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar yepiya re wekenonj Yuda eriya w…®ng…®r…®nd. ∆ó ton ket y…®pay…®pa r…®gap y…®samko wulk…®p oramkam towa wulk…®p r…®r…®r…®nd d…®de ongg…®tyam wulk…®p …®tm…®kitam towa p…®lwa.  
\v 30 ∆ó re ket ton wulk…®p emd…®to, ton ket akawo Banaba d…®de Saul towa p…®l…®nd iyoy…®m elda wa p…®lwa yepiya re Yerusalem taun…®nd wekenonj.   
\c 12  
\s1 Erod Yakobond Yongandonj d…®de Petrond S…®b…®bmet wa Yoramitonj  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd king Erod singi awonj Yerusalem sosi w…®ng…®r…®nd n…®nda r…®ga neg…®r omn…®kam. S…® ton ket tina danda ke n…®nda r…®ga emjinonj.  
\v 2 ∆ó ton kea Yoan…®mna nany Yakobond yokatonj, …® ket geja giri ke uj tama yongandonj.  
\v 3 S…® ongg…®t mop penaemb Ju r…®ga ma sobijog na sam auk…®to. ∆ó re Erod ongg…®tyam towaina sam y…®r yongonj, ton kwa y…®samkonj Petrond daka okatam. Ongg…®tyam m…®le aukonj re y…®pa Ju r…®ga waina Yist kesa Bred W…®n nat.  
\v 4 S…® re ton Petrond yokatonj, ton ket yoramitonj s…®b…®bmet wa. ∆ó Erod sikstin (16) geja r…®ga etm…®kisinonj s…®b…®bmet mopyam…®m p…®lwa danda k…®ma Petrond y…®r …®pkam, nok…®m da …®denat powa (4) geja r…®ga bobop sensi omnena k…®ma tin b'obog…®l y…®r …®pka iyenyi. ∆ó tina …®samki singi re …®ja naemb da ton Ju r…®ga waina Uj ∆ógwanti Nony Iyena Diyamdiyam W…®n kak ke Petrond yii dem r…®ga wa w…®p wa, …® tin onganj dem.  
\v 5 S…® ongg…®t penaemb geja r…®gap Petrond y…®r …®pka yiyeno s…®b…®bmet…®nd. Aj…® ongg…®t w…®n…®nd sosi r…®gap daka kea …®m…®njog gar ke ti gatab y…®r opmitento God…®m p…®lwa.   
\s1 Aneru Petrond Yopendonj S…®b…®bmet ke  
\p
\v 6 ∆ó ongg…®t s…®w…®ny…®nd re Erod singi awonj Petrond neg…®r omnam …®spari ke, Petro y…®t wegonj n…®mog geja r…®ga wa ganggand. ∆ó Petromna y…®pa y…®m re sein kai ke …®job…®ki na y…®bnonj y…®pa geja r…®gamna y…®m…®nd d…®de kwa y…®pa y…®m re odede y…®pa w…®p …®job…®ki na y…®bnonj kwa y…®pa geja r…®gamna y…®m…®nd. ∆ó daka n…®mog geja r…®gap onyiti na ongg…®t s…®b…®bmet y…®r …®pka yiyenonda mora dundand.  
\v 7 ∆ó odedend ket y…®pa Yonggyam…®mna aneru Petrom wus…®nd onyitonj, …® ngayat y…®nyomarenonj ongg…®tyam s…®b…®bmet w…®ng…®r…®nd. ∆ó ton ket Petrond y…®dbontonj yororand, d…®de ket tin yutunga ke yutnyitonj. ∆ó ket yomnonj da, ‚ÄúWanakana utnyite!‚Äù ∆ó odenja ket tina y…®m ke …®job…®ki sein kai b'…®trendonda.  
\v 8 ∆ó kwa aneru tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúMoina rob ke b'obog…®l b'…®job…®ke, d…®de moina yong…®nkak b'ikokine!‚Äù Seg Petro kea tina y…®t r…®r…®r…®nd amn…®kinonj. ∆ó aneru b'usaya kwa yomnonj da, ‚ÄúMoina tum…®nd iyenapu p…®np…®n kob…®rg…®m b'ikite, d…®de ken y…®mta nundoke!‚Äù  
\v 9 S…® Petro re aneru k…®ma na opendonj s…®b…®bmet ke, d…®de ket tin y…®mta yundokonj. ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd Petro maka nony aukonj da ongg…®t anerumna omn…®ki m…®le re …®m…®njog e. Aj…® …®ja na ton nony awonj da, ‚ÄúKon re liyalliyal gasa e y…®r yongen.‚Äù  
\v 10 ∆ó ton ket egoukisinonda naskajog s…®b…®bmet r…®ga y…®r …®pka r…®ga bobo d…®de kwa ket n…®mog…®m s…®b…®bmet r…®ga y…®r …®pka r…®ga bobo. ∆ó ongg…®tyam s…®b…®bmet kara y…®pa tab…®nd ay…®n ke omn…®ki mora y…®bnonj r…®ngkena re y…®pa taun…®m nya y…®bnonj. ∆ó re ton opendonda ongg…®tyam mora wa, mora tilenggyam b'…®pangendonj towan…®m. S…® ket ton opendonda ongg…®tyam mora ke. ∆ó ton menon yokatonda, d…®de opendonda de y…®pa ukoi nya wa. Seg, odenja ket anerut tin y…®raronj.  
\v 11 ∆ó …®ngkenaemb ket Petrond nony…®t yodarkonj, …® ket ton tina gar ke yindonj da, ‚ÄúOo, kemb kon …®m…®njog wum…®r aen da Yonggyam…®t kor n…®tm…®kitau Tina aneru, d…®de Ton ket kea ken n…®tr…®ngas Erod…®mna dandam p…®lke d…®de Ju r…®ga waina komkesa …®samki singi ke.‚Äù  
\v 12 ∆ó re ton odede yongwatonj, ton yikonj Yoan…®m mog Mariyamna met wa. R…®gap yogenayo ongg…®tyam r…®ga Yoan…®nd kwa y…®pa ny…® ke da Mak. ∆ó ongg…®t met…®nd re kea jogjog r…®ga bobo b'eomto, d…®de y…®r opmitena wuwenonj.  
\v 13 ∆ó Petro ket ongg…®tyam met kara mora yipowonj, …® ket y…®pa w…®ko ng…®mngai, ny…® da Rode, wikonj mora wa r…®ga ongwatam.  
\v 14 ∆ó ton ket kea Petro ma nonykok b'obog…®l yongwatonj, s…® ukoi sam na yokatonj. Ton maka mora y…®pangendonj Petrom b'…®garam, aj…® ton b'…®kok nena awonj met w…®ng…®r wa, …® ket r…®ga wum…®r amneninonj da, ‚ÄúPetro …®ta mora wa onyiti y…®b…®m.‚Äù  
\v 15 Aj…® r…®gap tin womno da, ‚ÄúMan kor…®rkor…®r e ainy…®t are!‚Äù Aj…® ton kea ongg…®tyam y…®t yusairenonj, …® danda k…®ma windonj da, ‚Äú∆óm…®njog e-o! Ma kon b'anyg…®neny…®n-a!‚Äù S…® todaka endento da, ‚ÄúAma r…®ka tina anerute.‚Äù  
\v 16 Aj…® Petro re omanda mora yipowayonj. S…® r…®gap ket wuwonj de mora wa, …® ket mora y…®pangendo, ng…®rpu ton ket Petrond y…®r yongo. S…® ton ma sobijog na k…®d kesa auk…®to.  
\v 17 ∆ó Petro ket y…®m ke r…®ga eswanginonj, …® ket towa usenenainonj r…®ja na re Yonggyam tin y…®tr…®ngatonj s…®b…®bmet ke. ∆ó ton ket ten amninonj da, ‚ÄúW…®n ongg…®tyam y…®t wum…®r oramitenya Yakobom p…®lwa d…®de kwa komkesa gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar wa p…®lwa.‚Äù Seg ton ket yiwatonj ongg…®t met ke, d…®de ket menon yokatonj b'enga gatab wa.   
\p
\v 18 ∆ó …®spari ke ket, geja r…®gap maka Petrond y…®r yongo. S…® towa w…®ng…®r…®nd ma sobijog na y…®t b'iklawa wuwenonj odede da, ‚ÄúNangga na aw…®k Petrom p…®l…®nd?‚Äù  
\v 19 Ongg…®t kak ke, Erod tin oraka yiyenonj, aj…® makwa yodaronj. S…® ton b'obog…®l erkena eyeninonj s…®b…®bmet y…®r …®pka r…®ga, aj…® makwa nangga b'og…®l m…®ra na yokatonj. S…® ton ket b'ingawa yoramitonj ten ongandam. Seg ket Erod Yuda eriya ke yiwatonj, …® ket yikonj Kaisareya wa w…®menam.   
\s1 Erod…®mna Uj gatab Y…®t  
\p
\v 20 ∆ó Erod re ma sobijog na soro aenonj Tiro ake Sidon r…®ga wa p…®lwa. Aj…® ongg…®t n…®mog eriya r…®ga waina owou wuwenonj re Erod…®mna kantri kena. S…® ongg…®t penaemb Tiro ake Sidon r…®gap y…®pand g…®lg…®l wuwonj Erod…®m p…®lwa Erod k…®ma ng…®mbla okatam. S…® ton naska king…®mna nony …®jai wungapu y…®r …®pka r…®ga Blastom p…®lwa wuwonj nony okatam da, ‚Äú∆ódenat ton sowa gatab wa tainy.‚Äù ∆ó d…®de ton ket tin yerkito ng…®mbla okatam king Erod k…®ma.  
\v 21 S…® Erod y…®pa bib…®r yobagendonj towan…®m y…®t opurenam. ∆ó re ongg…®tyam bib…®r yokatonj, Erod ket b'og…®l king kob…®rg…®m b'ikokinonj, d…®de ket omitonj king…®mna w…®p omnenapu kasand. ∆ó ton ket n…®nda y…®t apureninonj r…®ga wa p…®lwa yepiya re tuwonj Tiro ake Sidon ke.  
\v 22 ∆ó re ton y…®t opurena seg awonj, utkunda r…®ga bobop b'okta ara wuwenonj da, ‚Äú∆ótemb re ma r…®gaina opurena im, aj…® god…®mna opurena im!‚Äù  
\v 23 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd Erod maka God…®nd yesourenonj. S…® ongg…®t penaemb Yonggyam…®mna anerut odenja ti p…®l…®nd kopa yoramitonj. ∆ó ket kopa ogona kom kup…®r…®p tin ongong yiyeno, s…® ton ket uj awonj.   
\p
\v 24 Aj…® God ma y…®tkak re kea ukoi auka yikenonj, d…®de warabag auka yikenonj.  
\v 25 ∆ó re Banaba ake Saul towaina w…®ko seg yomnonda Yerusalem taun…®nd, ton yokatonda Yoan…®nd yena re kwa ny…® yogenayo da Mak, d…®de ket ton k…®ma …®tendonda Antiyok wa.   
\c 13  
\s1 Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat Abagendonj Banaba ake Saul  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó Antiyok sosi w…®ng…®r…®nd kea de wekenonj bageyam d…®de ouyaena r…®ga. S…® opimemb j…® r…®ga Banaba, …® Simeon yena re kwa ny…® yogenayo da Niger,\f + \fr 13:1 \ft Niger yis…®pkis re g…®m timtim e.\f* …® Kurene tunggam Lukiyo, …® king Erod k…®ma y…®pand ongeni r…®ga Manaen, …® d…®de Saul.  
\v 2 ∆ó re ton Yonggyam…®nd yewangaeneno d…®de owou uwab…®ka w…®n yokateneno, Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat kea ket ten amninonj da, ‚ÄúW…®n Banaba ake Saul Kor notkaya, mop nok…®p Kon…®t ten ara emokond Koina singi w…®ko omn…®kam.‚Äù  
\v 3 S…® ongg…®t penaemb ton ket owou uwab…®ka w…®n yokateno, …® y…®r opmitento. ∆ó ton ket towa p…®l…®nd y…®m aramk…®to ten danda okawam, ng…®rpu ket ten etm…®kito.   
\s1 Banaba ake Saul Towaina Menon Kipriyo wa  
\p
\v 4 ∆ó Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®ngat ten etm…®kitonj, s…® ton ekonda de Selyukiya wa. S…® …®ngkenaemb ton ket g…®ga yokatonda d…®de ket ekonda Kipriyo ailan wa.  
\v 5 ∆ó re ton opendonda ailan …®le tab ke Salami taun wa, ton ket ekenonda Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met nata God ma y…®t p…®tap…®ta omnenam. ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd towa y…®m b'akawa r…®ga Yoan, …® yama re y…®pa ny…® da Mak, omanda ton k…®ma yikenonj.  
\v 6 ∆ó ket ton ongg…®t kupka ailan w…®ng…®r nata wuwenonj, ng…®rpu opento de ailan kemag gatab ke Papo taun wa. ∆ó ton ket ademb de y…®r yongo y…®pa Ju r…®ga ny…® da Bayesu. Ton re mikujam na d…®de b'anyg…®nena bageyam na y…®bnonj.  
\v 7 ∆ó ton re kwa ita w…®n…®nd Roma gabmani mopyam Sergiyo Paulo k…®ma na y…®bnenonj. ∆ó Sergiyo Paulo re b'og…®l multek…®p r…®ga e. S…® ton ket engaukonj Banaba ake Saul, nok…®p ton singi na God ma y…®t utkundam towa p…®lke.  
\v 8 Aj…® re Banaba ake Saul tetkonda ti p…®lwa, mikujam Bayesu yaina Grik y…®t ke engendi ny…® re kwa Elima, ten agokinonj God ma y…®t usekam Sergiyo Paulom p…®lwa. Mop nok…®p ton singi na da …®denat Sergiyo Paulo maka Yesund gar ke utkunda ke okas.  
\v 9 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd omandemb Saul, kwa y…®pa ti ny…® re Pol, Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga ke y…®ndang…®r aukonj, d…®de ton ket Elimam p…®lwa y…®r …®sokonj.  
\v 10 ∆ó ton ket tin yomnonj da, ‚ÄúMan, Satanamna b'…®ga! Man re komkesa b'anyg…®nena m…®le ke d…®de komkesa neg…®rjog m…®le ke y…®ndang…®r omni et. W…®i, man komkesa neg…®r kesa d…®md…®mjog m…®lemna geja r…®ga et! Man ita w…®n…®nd dadal dadal Yonggyam…®mna d…®md…®mjog ouyaena y…®t b'anyg…®nena nya ke kaokao amn…®keneniny…®t. Ma man singi et odede neg…®r m…®le d…®k…®nd seg omny…®t?  
\v 11 S…® ongg…®t paemb da Yonggyam…®mna danda y…®m re ke mor kumb nate ainy. ∆ó man otade …®ta y…®rd…®d…® tauket, ng…®rpu rokate ra God…®mna obagendi w…®n okas dem. ∆ó ma …®ta ket lomkongga ngaya ongwateny…®t y…®r ongong…®m.‚Äù ∆ó y…®t seg ke odenja temat tin y…®r y…®kang…®ndonj, …® ket ton y…®r s…®b…®b awonj. S…® ongg…®t penaemb ton y…®r tumtum yikenonj, d…®de r…®ga oraka eyeninonj tin y…®m otona iyoy…®m.  
\v 12 ∆ó ongg…®t w…®n…®nd Sergiyo Paulo kea ongg…®tyam auki m…®le y…®r yongonj, d…®de ton ket ma sobijog na k…®d kesa aenonj ongg…®tyam Yonggyam…®mna ouyaeni danda y…®tkak gatab. S…® ton ket Yonggyam…®nd gar ke utkunda ke yokatonj.   
\s1 Pol ake Banaba Ekonda Antiyok Taun wa Pisidiya Eriyand  
\p
\v 13 ∆ó Pol ti r…®gawar k…®ma g…®ga yokato, …® ket yiwato Papo taun ke, ng…®rpu wuwonj de Perga taun wa Pampiliya eriyand. Aj…® ongg…®t w…®n…®nd Yoan Mak re ademb de ten eraronj, …® ket …®tendonj Yerusalem taun wa.  
\v 14 ∆ó Pol ake Banaba ket Perga taun ke yiwatonda, d…®de ket opendonda de Antiyok taun wa Pisidiya eriyand. S…® re Ju r…®ga waina w…®ram d…®de y…®r opmitena bib…®r awonj, ton ket b'…®garonda Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met w…®ng…®r wa, …® ket omitonda.  
\v 15 ∆ó re ogenka r…®gap ogenka seg auk…®to Mosemna peba ke d…®de n…®nda bageyam waina peba ke, Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met y…®r …®pka mopyam r…®gap y…®t etm…®kitawo Pol ake Banaba towa p…®lwa da, ‚ÄúW…®n, sowa r…®ga! Rada opima wa p…®l…®nd wekeny n…®nda b'ugowa y…®t r…®ga wa p…®lwa p…®tap…®ta omnenam, s…® s…®n wa maemb ket gangga takau opurenam.‚Äù  
\v 16 S…® Pol utnyitonj d…®de yikonj w…®p wa. ∆ó ton ket y…®m ke r…®ga eswanginonj, d…®de ket y…®t b'atomonj da,  
\p ‚ÄúKor r…®gawar! Israel r…®ga d…®de kwa God…®nd ewangaya God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga,\f + \fr 13:16 \ft Ton re God…®mna obag…®ki kesa r…®ga im, aj…® ton engento Ju r…®ga waina m…®le wa God…®nd ewangayam.\f* w…®n ken nutkunda!  
\v 17 Ongg…®t Israel r…®gaina God…®t meraina b'uwar abagenjinonj. ∆ó re opimemb r…®ga Ejipt kantrind obayam wekenonj, God kea towa ukoi danda akainonj, d…®de ten ukoi warabag amn…®kinonj. Ongg…®t kak ke Ton ukoi danda y…®m yoramitonj Ejipt kantrind, d…®de ket ten apenjinonj ongg…®t kantri ke.  
\v 18 Seg ket re ton wul kesa tungg…®nd wekenonj poti (40) kemag k…®ma, ton ma sobijog na neg…®r m…®le amn…®kenento God…®m w…®p…®nd. Aj…® God kea ongg…®tyam towaina neg…®r m…®le gatab mus…®k w…®mena nena na yokatenonj.  
\v 19 Ongg…®t kak ke ket, God neg…®r amn…®kinonj seben (7) y…®tam r…®ga r…®na re wekenonj Kanaan gow…®nd, …® ongg…®tyam towaina gou sowa b'uwar Israel r…®ga wa akainonj owab…®ntam.  
\v 20 Ongg…®t kak ke, God towa akainonj b'…®sag…®ka r…®ga powa andred pipti (450) kemag k…®ma,\f + \fr 13:20 \ft N…®nda r…®gap endenanj da ongg…®tyam powa andred pipti (450) kemag re Israel b'uwar waina Ejipt wa opendipu d…®de Kanaan gou okatipu kemag gangga e.\f* ng…®rpu ongg…®t w…®n…®nd re Samuwel bageyam ny…® yeb…®m.  
\v 21 ∆ó re Samuwel bageyam y…®bnonj, odedend r…®gap tin yerkito y…®pa king obagendam ten w…®p omnenam. S…® God akainonj Benyamin gu ke r…®ga Kis…®mna b'…®ga Saul. S…® Saul ket poti (40) kemag k…®ma ten w…®p amninonj.  
\v 22 ∆ó re God Saul…®nd yewaikitonj, Ton ket Dawid…®nd yonyitonj towa king…®m. ∆ó God kea ti gatab y…®r ungata y…®t yindenonj odede da, ‚ÄòRe Kon Yesaimna b'…®ga Dawid…®nd y…®r yongond, ton re Koina gar ke nony …®jai r…®ga e. ∆ó tonte dem Koina komkesa singi gasa tamn…®kiny dem.‚Äô  
\v 23 ∆ó God re kea t…®r…®r y…®t Dawid…®nd yomnonj da, ‚ÄòKon …®ta moina kus b'…®gam p…®lke y…®rkokar okawa r…®ga takainy…®n dem Israel r…®ga wa.‚Äô S…® God Tina t…®r…®r omni y…®t r…®r…®r…®nd ongg…®tyam y…®rkokar okawa r…®ga Yesund yoramitonj Israel r…®ga wa p…®lwa.  
\v 24 ∆ó ket Yoan naska nata gar engenda baptiso p…®tap…®ta amneninonj komkesa Israel r…®ga wa p…®lwa. S…® …®ngkenaemb ket Yesu ikonj tina b'angonjeni lomena tum nata.  
\v 25 Re Yoan momta tina w…®ko undwatam yomnonj, ton yindonj da, ‚ÄòW…®n r…®ja im nony aindam yeten kon? Kon ma Kerisoten yena re w…®n y…®r yungaya. Aj…® y…®r de, …®ta Ton kor kak ke ik, s…® kon makwa r…®r…®r en Tina goujog w…®ko r…®ga p…®la Tina yong…®nkak kai …®trekam.‚Äô   
\p
\v 26 ‚ÄúKor r…®gawar! Abraam…®mna b'usmureni b'…®gawar d…®de kwa God…®nd ewangaya God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga, w…®n wum…®r yokata! God ke ongg…®tyam y…®rkokar okawa y…®t y…®tm…®kitonj mera p…®lwa.  
\v 27 ∆ó r…®ga yepiya re wekenonj Yerusalem taun…®nd d…®de towaina w…®p iyoi r…®gap maka Yesund yongwato da Ton re Keriso e. ∆ó ton kwa maka nony aukenento Yesum gatab bageyam waina y…®t r…®na re ton agenkenento ita towaina w…®ram d…®de y…®r opmitena bib…®r…®nd. S…® Ti gatab wum…®r kesand, ton neg…®r ma b'…®sag…®ka m…®le yomn…®ko Tin ongandam. S…® odede nya ke, ongg…®tyam towaina m…®let kemb bageyam waina y…®t r…®r…®rk…®p yomnonj.  
\v 28 D…®de kwa ton makwa y…®pa Ti ongandam r…®l yodarawo, aj…® ton Pilatond yerkito Tin ongandam r…®l kesa.  
\v 29 ∆ó re Ton uj awonj wul kumb…®nd, r…®gap Tin gou wa yomno ongg…®t wul kumb ke, d…®de gopmet wa yoramito. S…® odede towaina m…®le ke re kemb komkesa Ti gatab …®r…®ki y…®tkak r…®r…®rk…®p auto.  
\v 30 Aj…® God…®t Tin yutnyitonj uj ke.  
\v 31 Seg ket jogjog bib…®r k…®ma Yesu Tina utnyiti j…® auyaeninonj towa p…®lwa r…®ga yepiya re naskand ton k…®ma wuwenonj Galili ke de Yerusalem taun wa. S…® ton re Tina utnyita gatab y…®r ungata r…®ga im r…®ga wa w…®p…®nd p…®tap…®ta omnenam.  
\v 32 ∆ó s…®da kwa yu wa p…®lwa p…®tap…®ta yomnenyu God ma b'og…®l y…®rkokar bage y…®t r…®na re God sowaina b'uwar wa t…®r…®r y…®t akainonj.  
\v 33 S…®n opimemb re towaina b'…®ga im. ∆ó God…®t Yesund yutnyitonj uj ke, s…® …®ngkenaemb ket ongg…®tyam Tina t…®r…®r omni y…®t r…®r…®rk…®p yomnonj sowan…®m. ∆ó kwa …®ja emb j…® Tina utnyita gatab …®r…®ki y…®b…®m Ger Peba n…®mog…®m saptand da,  
\q1 ‚ÄòMan re Kor b'…®ga et,  
\q2 yu Kon kemb p…®tap…®ta momny…®n da Man re Kor b'…®ga et.‚Äô   
\m
\v 34 ∆ó God Tin yutnyitonj uj ke, nok…®m da …®denat Ton maka t…®tenj …®tk…®kam. S…® ongg…®t gatab y…®na pebat …®ja emb j…® yindeny da, ‚ÄòKon opima wa takainy…®n b'og…®l gasa r…®na re Kon y…®nay…®na omni d…®de …®m…®njog omni k…®ma t…®r…®r y…®t yomnond Dawid…®nd.‚Äô  
\v 35 S…® ongg…®t penaemb Dawid Ger Peba b'enga saptand yindonj God…®m p…®lwa da, ‚ÄòMan ma …®ta Moina Y…®na R…®gand …®tk…®ki y…®r onget dem.‚Äô  
\v 36 ∆ó re Dawid y…®bnonj ti yilond, ton kea God…®mna singi w…®ko amn…®keninonj. Aj…® ongg…®t kak ke ket, ton uj awonj, d…®de ti b'uwar waina gopmet wa yoramito, …® ket tina ujg…®m kea …®tk…®konj.  
\v 37 Aj…® daka yena re God yutnyitonj uj ke, Ton maka …®tk…®konj.  
\v 38 Kor r…®gawar! Ongg…®t paemb kon y…®tkak p…®tap…®ta tamniny…®n ongg…®t R…®ga gatab, s…® w…®n b'ogla j…® wum…®r yokata. S…® …®temb j…® y…®tkak. Yepiya ra w…®n ongg…®t uj ke utnyiti R…®ga Yesund gar ke utkunda ke okasya, …®ngkaimemb God waina neg…®r m…®le aw…®r tamniny. ∆ó kwa w…®n komkesa makwa r…®r…®r im neg…®r kesa d…®md…®mjog r…®ga ny…® okatam Mosemna gog y…®t y…®mta undoka ke, mop nok…®p w…®n ma r…®r…®r im ongg…®tyam komkesa Mosemna gog y…®t y…®mta undokam.  
\v 39 Aj…® komkesa r…®ga yepiya ra …®temb r…®ga Yesund gar ke utkunda ke okasi, God opima towa takainy neg…®r kesa d…®md…®mjog r…®ga ny…®.  
\v 40 S…® ongg…®t paemb da w…®n y…®r k…®ma tekeny…®t! ∆ó ongg…®tyam m…®le goro ket wa p…®l…®nd raukinem ongg…®t bageyam…®mna opureni y…®tkak.  
\v 41 S…® …®ja emb j…® bageyam yindeny da,  
\q1 ‚ÄòW…®n yepiya re Koina y…®t …®sadrena yiyenonda. W…®n y…®r de!  
\q2 W…®n opima k…®d kesa tainindam dem, …® kwa w…®n opima neg…®r taukindam dem.  
\q1 Mop nok…®p ra waina w…®n ik dem, Kontemb y…®pa gasa omn…®ken,  
\q2 aj…® w…®n ma opima gar ke okasya dem ongg…®tyam gasa, nangga ma j…® rada y…®pa r…®gat wen wum…®r tamneniny dem.‚Äô‚Äù   
\p
\v 42 S…® re Pol ake Banaba opendonda ongg…®t met w…®ng…®r ke, r…®gap ket ten egekitto ongg…®tyam y…®tkak usenenam kwa y…®pa Ju r…®ga waina w…®ram d…®de y…®r opmitena bib…®r…®nd.  
\v 43 ∆ó towaina y…®r opmita seg ke, re r…®ga wetaweta auk…®to, jogjog Ju r…®ga d…®de God…®nd ewangaya God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga yepiya re engk…®to Ju r…®ga waina m…®le wa, ton ket y…®mta undoko Pol ake Banaba. S…® Pol ake Banaba ongg…®t r…®ga k…®ma y…®t b'usenena ekonda, d…®de danda k…®ma ten ugoinonda da, ‚ÄúW…®n b'ogla ita w…®n…®nd w…®mena tuweny…®t God…®mna wurar k…®ma.‚Äù   
\p
\v 44 ∆ó y…®pa sande kak ke, re Ju r…®ga waina w…®ram d…®de y…®r opmitena bib…®r awonj, ama r…®ka momta komkesa Antiyok taun r…®ga b'eomkurto Yonggyam…®mna y…®tkak utkundam.  
\v 45 Aj…® re Ju r…®gap y…®r angto opimemb ukoi r…®ga bobo, s…® towaina gar re kea neg…®r y…®r ke y…®r ongong m…®le ke y…®ndang…®r auk…®to. ∆ó ongg…®t penaemb ton ket Pol…®mna opureni God ma y…®tkak …®sadrena k…®ma neg…®rjog opurena yiyeno.  
\v 46 S…® Pol ake Banaba daka moga kesa danda k…®ma ten amneninonda da, ‚ÄúS…®n b'ogla God ma y…®t naska opurena teyeninya w…®n Ju r…®ga wa p…®lwa. Aj…® w…®n walenggyam kea God ma y…®t ewaikenindam, d…®de w…®n walenggyam b'…®sag…®ka ke yoenya ng…®rpu kesa dadal y…®rkokar okatam. S…® ongg…®t paiemb s…®n yu wa p…®lke w…®p tengenjya God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga wa p…®lwa.  
\v 47 Mop nok…®p …®ja naemb j…® Yonggyam s…®n ningainonj da,  
\q1 ‚ÄòKon ket men motramis…®n God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga wa …®nyowayam y…®pa ngaya.  
\q2 S…® man b'ogla warabag omn…®ka iyeny…®t y…®rkokar okawam y…®tkak ng…®rpu de gowukoi ng…®rpu wa.‚Äô‚Äù   
\m
\v 48 S…® re God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®gap towaina y…®t utkundo, ton kea gar sam auk…®to, d…®de Yonggyam…®mna y…®tkak yesoureno. ∆ó komkesa r…®ga yena re God abag…®kinonj dadal ng…®rpu kesa y…®rkokar okawam, ton kea Yesund gar ke yokato.  
\v 49 ∆ó ket ongg…®tyam Yonggyam…®mna y…®tkak kea kupka ongg…®t eriya nata warabag auka yikenonj.  
\v 50 Aj…® Ju r…®gap God…®nd ewangaya ukoi ny…® kongga d…®de ongg…®t taun w…®ng…®r…®nd ukoi ny…® r…®ga …®l ongka eyento soro k…®ma ten neg…®r omn…®kam. S…® ket ongg…®t r…®gap soro k…®ma ow…®nk…®to Pol ake Banaba towa p…®lwa, d…®de ket neg…®r k…®ma b'…®dgotnena m…®le yoramiteno towa p…®l…®nd. ∆ó d…®de ton ket ten eaukeno towaina eriya ke.  
\v 51 S…® ongg…®t penaemb Pol ake Banaba towaina p…®spam…®nd k…®l b'…®dbenenonda towan…®m nony aukam da b'…®sag…®ka w…®n …®ta ik dem. Seg ton ket yiwatonda Ikoniyon taun wa.  
\v 52 Aj…® b'auyaena r…®ga yepiya re wekenonj Antiyok taun…®nd, ton ma sobijog na gar sam d…®de Y…®nay…®na W…®ngaw…®nga ke y…®ndang…®r na auk…®to.   
\c 14  
\s1 Pol ake Banaba Towaina Menon Ikoniyon wa  
\p
\v 1 ∆ó Pol ake Banaba towaina get ke m…®le ebnawonj re …®ja emb j…®, ra ton menon okasya y…®pa tungg wa, ton adea naska ekenenonda Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met wa Ju r…®ga odaram. S…® ongg…®t penaemb re ton y…®pand opendonda Ikoniyon taun wa, ton ket b'…®garonda Ju r…®ga waina y…®r opmitenapu met wa, d…®de ket apureninonda God ma y…®tkak. S…® ukoijog r…®ga bobo, Ju r…®ga d…®de Grik r…®gap Yesund gar ke utkunda ke yokato.  
\v 2 Aj…® n…®nda Ju r…®ga yepiya re b'…®saito Yesund gar ke utkunda ke okatam, ton God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®ga y…®t amnento soro k…®ma ow…®nkam Pol ake Banaba d…®de gar ke utkunda nany d…®de y…®ngganwar wa p…®lwa. ∆ó …®ngkenaemb ket n…®nda God ma obag…®ki kesa r…®gap neg…®r nony menamena akatento towa p…®lwa.  
\v 3 S…® ongg…®t penaemb Pol ake Banaba p…®njog w…®mena yokatenonda demb de ongg…®t taun…®nd. ∆ó ongg…®t beb…®g w…®n…®nd, ton ket moga kesa Yonggyam Yesumna wurar y…®tkak danda k…®ma p…®tap…®ta amneninonda y…®tkak …®m…®njog ke okatam. S…® towaina y…®tkak p…®tap…®ta omnena w…®ng…®r…®nd, Yonggyam daka kea agoninonj k…®d kesa k…®ma danda w…®ko d…®de moga k…®ma danda w…®ko towaina y…®m ke aukam.  
