\v 12 ∆ó ton ket Banaband ny…® yogenayo y…®pa towaina god ma ny…® ke da ‚ÄúJeus‚Äù.\f + \fr 14:12 \ft Grik r…®gap jogjog god na …®m…®njog…®m amnento. ∆ó Jeus re towaina y…®pa ukoijog w…®p omnena god na.\f* ∆ó Pol…®nd daka kwa y…®pa towaina god ma ny…® ke yogenayo da ‚ÄúErme‚Äù\f + \fr 14:12 \ft Grik r…®gap …®m…®njog ke yomneno Ermend da ton re bageyam god e n…®nda god wa.\f* mop nok…®p ton re y…®t opurena mopyam r…®ga na.  
